==================
README for RunTask
==================

Installing
==========

Use ``setup.py``::

    python setup.py build
    sudo python setup.py install


Reading the docs
================

After installing::

    cd doc
    sphinx-build . _build/html

Then, direct your browser to ``_build/html/index.html``.

Or read them online at <http://opendcf77.inrim.it/runtask>.


